### 🔴 FUNCTIONAL BUG CONFIRMED: Picker Click-to-Select Does NOT Work

**Test Environment:**
- Page: http://192.168.43.133:8790/#/picker
- Browser: Chrome (desktop mode)
- Picker Type: Mint UI inline Picker components (3 separate pickers visible on page)

---

